 "components": {
  "task_instruction": "You are a precise text classifier. Read the input text and assign it to exactly one of the categories defined below.",
  "label::automatic_top_up": "",
  "label::balance_not_updated_after_bank_transfer": "Questions or issues about a transfer that has been made but the account balance does not yet reflect the transfer, including concerns about delays or missing funds after sending money. Use this when the user is waiting for a received bank transfer to be shown in their balance, not when they are asking in general how long a transfer takes or about transfer processing times. If the user is asking generally about expected timing (not about a specific event or missing funds), use 'transfer_timing'.",
